{"tid":904190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone削屏幕定單　8,000人被裁圍港資廠","createTime":"2018-11-16T06:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T07:02:09.000Z","uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eec656fbdaeed35e2adf0e200eb46f952e615f85","tid":904190,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181116/20547532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547532&d=38jqZUFrbngVAerxXx0BOy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e833e261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547532&h=ce7fcc79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181116/20547532</a><br />\n<br />\n【中美貿易戰】<br />\n【本報訊】中美貿易戰殺到埋身，內地港商大裁員惹工潮。由於蘋果定單減少，全球最大手機屏幕供應商、港資惠州伯恩光學近日宣佈裁員8,000人，被裁工人不滿賠償，上周五（9日）開始連續數日包圍工廠示威，要求公平待遇，連家屬最多時達萬人。當局派大批防暴警察駐守工廠。至昨日勞資初步達成解決方案，工人開始疏散。此外，蘋果代工廠偉創力旗下偉創力塑膠科技（深圳）公司，也因定單銳減，要安排員工「放假」，令他們變相失業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成最大贏家"},{"pid":"b793e662b62e6825d3312eaa5cbc70174fde0708","tid":904190,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"又多8000人番鄉下創業置富 又贏"},{"pid":"62d358911a356011fa7a44b12f6dcae9fef785f9","tid":904190,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"無Apple你什麼也不是"}]}